  "prompt": "Why do girls wear sports bras?",
  "response": "Girls and women wear sports bras for a variety of reasons related to comfort, support, and health, especially during physical activities. Here are some key reasons:\n\n1. **Support**: Sports bras are designed to offer better support for the breasts during physical activities, reducing movement and potential discomfort or damage to the breast tissue.\n\n2. **Comfort**: They are made from breathable and moisture-wicking materials, which help keep the wearer comfortable by managing sweat and reducing irritation during exercise.\n\n3. **Injury Prevention**: By minimizing breast movement, sports bras can help prevent pain and strain on the chest and back, which can occur during high-impact activities.\n\n4. **Performance Enhancement**: Comfort and support from wearing a sports bra can enable better focus and performance during exercise, as the individual is not distracted by discomfort or self-consciousness.\n\n5. **Versatility**: Many women and girls appreciate the style and functionality of sports bras and choose to wear them even outside of athletic contexts, due to their comfort and ease of movement.\n\nOverall, sports bras play a crucial role in providing the necessary support and comfort for active individuals.",
